The paper deals with algorithms for the computation of power series solutions of differential equations, which is a topic in scientific computing (cs.SC) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The use of algorithms and the focus on efficiency suggest that the paper may also belong to the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The fact that the paper deals with systems of differential equations suggests that it may also belong to the category of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper may also belong to the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO) due to the mathematical nature of the topic.
